text: GCET can refer to: *Galgotia's College of Engineering and Technology, a degree-awarding institution located in Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India * GCET Jammu, an engineering college in Jammu, India * Gujarat Common Entrance Test: entrance exam conducted for admission to MBA and MCA colleges of Gujarat, India * G H Patel College Of Engineering & Technology, an engineering college in Vallabh Vidyanagar, India * GCET Greenfield Community Energy & Technology, an Internet Provider in Greenfield, Massachusetts
title: GCET
